summary: An Ordinance accepting a deed from Oscar G. Heaton and Viola F. Heaton, his wife, of Seattle, Washington, to the City of Seattle, dated the 18th day of February, 1908, to Lots Four (4), Six (6) and Eight (8) Less the west two feet of Lot Eight (8) in Block Nine (9) of Craven's Division of Green Lake Addition to Seattle, the same to be used for Park and Parkway purposes.
